                <head>[Memorandum.]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Embassy of the French Republic</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-07-20">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 20, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Referring to a recent conversation, the charge d’affaires of France has the honor
                    to state that he has been invited to make known to the Government of the United
                    States that the Government of the Republic is disposed to concert with the
                    powers in the precautions to be taken to prevent the shipment of arms which
                    should be destined for China.</p>
            </div>
